  "title": "Accounts Assistant (Partial Set)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Accounts Assistant (F&B Industry) </strong></p><p>Working Days: Monday to Friday 8.30am to 6pm<br />Working Location: Woodlands Link [Nearest: Admiralty MRT]<br />Salary: $2300 – $2600</p><p><strong>Job scope</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare Audit schedule</li><li>Processing all invoices</li><li>checking on daily salesman report of sales</li><li>Perform data entry and other adhoc duties</li><li>Record payments, invoices, and journal entries into the accounting system</li><li>Review and verify monthly petty cash statements and claims</li><li>Maintain daily cash book schedules, monitor cash flow and balances, and perform bank reconciliations</li></ul><p><strong>Requirement</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Accounting</li><li>Min, 3-4 years of experience in bookkeeping</li><li>Familiar with MS Dynamic 365</li><li>Proficient in Ms Excel</li></ul><p><strong>Tee Xin Li Reg No: R24121619</strong><br /><strong>The Supreme Hr Advisory Pte Ltd EA No: 14C7279</strong></p>",
